cronjobs:
    triggering types: 
        fixed time cycle 
        dynamic
        manual
        workflow based cycle (dependent triggers)

    components:
        time setting 
        system prompt 
        triggering data ingestions (real time/or manual)
        scripts 
        output structure 

    Internal triggers:
        certain cronjobs events would trigger internal (ai os) system like data saving or modifying certain components of ai os.      
